audio music "res://BGM/坂の上の陽炎 - morning 2.mp3"
# Scene 1: Morning Wake-Up
# Setting: Rin's bedroom, 8:00 AM
# Theme: Establishing care and emotional connection
[background arg="res://Assets/Noraneko_Backgrounds_Pack_2/Noraneko_Backgrounds_Pack_2/Bedroom_Night_Dark.png" fade="1.5" wait="true"]
[background arg="res://Assets/Noraneko_Backgrounds_Pack_2/Noraneko_Backgrounds_Pack_2/Bedroom_Day.png" fade="1.5" wait="true"]

"The morning light filters through the curtains."
narrator: Her face looks peaceful. She's still asleep.

- Let her sleep a bit longer
	narrator: You quietly leave the room, letting her rest.
	narrator: Time passes. You return at 9\:00 AM.
	[signal arg="time:+1"]
	join Asami center [animation="Slide From Left" length="2.0" wait="true"]
	Asami: Oh... I slept longer than I meant to.
	Asami: I'm sorry. I know you wanted to have breakfast together...
	Don't apologize. Your health comes first.
	update Asami [extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Happy1"]
	Asami: ...
	Asami: You're too kind to me.
	narrator: "There's relief in her voice."
	[signal arg="affection:+2"]
	[signal arg="mood:calm"]
	leave Asami [animation="Fade Out" length="0.3"]
	jump scene_01_morning_wakeup/breakfast_choice:

- Gently call her name
	player: Rin... good morning.
	[signal arg="time:+1"]
	join Asami center [animation="Slide From Left" length="2.5" wait="true"]
	Asami: Mm... Good morning...
	Asami: What time is it?
	player: Eight o'clock. How do you feel today?
	Asami: A bit tired, but... I'm okay.
	Asami: You're always checking on me first thing.
	Asami: That's sweet.
	narrator: "Rin stretches gently, careful not to strain herself."
	[signal arg="affection:+3"]
	[signal arg="mood:calm"]
	leave Asami [animation="Fade Out" length="0.3"]
	jump scene_01_morning_wakeup/breakfast_choice:

- Check her health first
	Let me check how you're feeling first.
	"You gently place a hand on her forehead."
	"She stirs slightly."
	[signal arg="time:+1"]
	join Asami center [animation="Fade In" wait="true" extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Surprised1"]
	Asami: Ah! You startled me.
	Asami: ...Is everything okay?
	player: Just wanted to make sure you're not running a fever.
	update Asami [extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Smile1"]
	Asami: You worry too much.
	Asami: I'm alright. My body's just... always tired.
	player: That's why I'm going to find the Elixir.
	update Asami [extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Sad1"]
	Asami: .....
	Asami: I know.
	Asami: I don't want you to have to risk your life for me...
	Asami: But I'm grateful you're here.
	"The weight of your quest settles on you both."
	[signal arg="affection:+5"]
	[signal arg="mood:touched"]
	leave Asami
	jump scene_01_morning_wakeup/breakfast_choice:

label breakfast_choice:
[background arg="res://Assets/Noraneko_Background_Pack_1/Noraneko_Background_Pack_1/Sitting_Room.png" fade="0.0"]

"Rin's stomach reminds you both that breakfast is needed."
"What will you prepare?"

- Cook her favorite — a grand meal (3000g)
	[signal arg="mood:very_happy"]
	[signal arg="meal:grand"]
	"You spend an hour preparing Rin's favorite meal."
	narrator: Roasted vegetables, fresh bread, herbal tea infused with honey.
	[signal arg="time:+1"]
	join Asami center [animation="Fade In" wait="true" extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Surprised1"]
	Asami: Oh wow... you really went all out.
	Asami: This looks amazing!
	player: Eat as much as you can. You need your strength.
	update Asami [extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Happy1"]
	Asami: Thank you.
	"She eats slowly but genuinely enjoys every bite."
	jump scene_01_morning_wakeup/end_breakfast:

- Make something simple and warm (1000g)
	[signal arg="mood:content"]
	[signal arg="meal:simple"]
	"You prepare a simple breakfast — warm bread, cheese, and mild broth."
	[signal arg="time:+1"]
	join Asami center [animation="Fade In" wait="true" extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Happy1"]
	Asami: This is nice. Thank you.
	player: Just eat at your own pace.
	Asami: I will. It's warm and comforting.
	jump scene_01_morning_wakeup/end_breakfast:

- Order takeout from town (1500g)
	[signal arg="affection:-2"]
	[signal arg="mood:sad"]
	[signal arg="meal:takeout"]
	"You order food from the local shop in town."
	"It arrives warm, but store-bought."
	[signal arg="time:+1"]
	join Asami center [animation="Fade In" wait="true" extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Annoyed2"]
	Asami: Again...?
	update Asami [extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Annoyed1"]
	Asami: Don't you think we could cook together sometimes?
	player: I wanted to let you rest.
	update Asami [extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Sad1"]
	Asami: I know, but... I miss cooking with you.
	Asami: It makes me feel like I'm still useful.
	player: You're always useful to me, Rin.
	update Asami [extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Smile1"]
	Asami: ...Thanks.
	jump scene_01_morning_wakeup/end_breakfast:

- Skip breakfast and go explore
	[signal arg="affection:-3"]
	[signal arg="mood:worried"]
	[signal arg="meal:skip"]
	[signal arg="rin_health:-5"]
	"You're eager to get to the dungeons."
	Asami: Every day counts toward finding the cure.
	join Asami center [animation="Fade In" wait="true" extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Sad1"]
	Asami: You're leaving already?
	Asami: You haven't eaten...
	player: I'll grab something in town. You should rest.
	I might comeback late
	You should cook for yourself for now
	update Asami [extra_data="set CharacterOffset/Expressions/Smile1"]
	Asami: Mhmm..
	Asami: Please be careful out there.
	Asami: Come home safe.
	player: I will. I promise.
	jump scene_01_morning_wakeup/end_breakfast:

label end_breakfast:

leave Asami
"After breakfast, you gather your gear."
"The dungeon awaits."
"Rin watches you prepare, a mix of hope and worry in her eyes."
"You step out into the morning air."
"Another day, another chance to find what she needs."
[background arg="res://Assets/Noraneko_Background_Pack_1/Gate_to_the_Netherworld_29.webp" fade="0.0"]
[signal arg="show_location_card:abyss"]